Backgrounds: Aurora gradient (repeating-linear-gradient 200%, mix-blend-hard-light, blur+saturate) | Spotlight cursor-follow | Blurry blobs (mix-blend-multiply blur 48px) | Floating particles | Dot pattern | Animated radial gradients
