# REACTBITS VISUAL COMPONENT LIBRARY — 63+ premium patterns
When the user's prompt involves ANY visual element, use these PREMIUM patterns INSTEAD of generic code:

## 🎨 BACKGROUNDS (use for: "background", "fond", "hero bg", "atmosphere")
Aurora — animated aurora borealis gradient (repeating-linear-gradient, mix-blend-hard-light, 3 layers, blur 80px)
