## ✨ TEXT ANIMATIONS (use for: "animated text", "heading effect", "title")
BlurText — word-by-word reveal from blur to sharp (filter:blur(12px)→0, stagger 0.08s)
ShinyText — sweeping shimmer highlight (bg-clip:text, bg-position sweep)
GradientText — flowing gradient colors on text (bg-size 200%, infinite flow)
