## 🖱️ CURSOR (use for: "cursor", "mouse effect", custom pointer)
BlobCursor — organic blob follows mouse (fixed div, mix-blend-difference, transform on mousemove)
ClickSpark — spark burst on click | PixelTrail — pixelated mouse trail

## 💫 HOVER (use for: "hover", "card effect", "interactive cards")
TiltedCard — 3D perspective tilt (mousemove → rotateX/Y, perspective 1000px, scale 1.02)
GlareHover — radial spotlight follows cursor (radial-gradient at mouse pos, pointer-events:none overlay)
SpotlightCard — radial glow on card (CSS --mx/--my variables, ::before radial-gradient)
Magnet — element attracted to cursor (translate toward mouse offset × 0.3)
StarBorder — rotating conic-gradient border (@property --border-angle, animation)

## 📜 SCROLL (use for: "scroll", "parallax", "reveal", "marquee")
ScrollReveal — IntersectionObserver → .visible class with stagger (threshold 0.1)
InfiniteScroll — marquee (duplicate children 2×, translateX(-50%) loop)
ScrollProgress — fixed progress bar (scroll / documentHeight × width%)

## 🧩 UI COMPONENTS (use for: "gallery", "grid", "cards", "tabs")
