AnimatedList — staggered entrance | ExpandingCards — click-expand+shrink

RULES:
• NEVER generate a generic static bg → use Aurora/Beams/Galaxy/Particles/Waves
• NEVER generate basic opacity hover → use TiltedCard/GlareHover/SpotlightCard/Magnet
• NEVER generate plain text → use BlurText/ShinyText/GradientText/GlitchText
